[Unit]
Description=Watch Nix System Unit Profile Changes

[Path]
PathChanged=/nix/var/nix/profiles/default/lib/systemd/system
PathChanged=/nix/var/nix/profiles/default/lib/systemd/user

[Install]
WantedBy=multi-user.target
